dct_title_s: Map of the River Gambia for 105 miles above the falls of Barraconda
dct_description_sm: by F.W. Finden ; from a sketch made by His Excellency Governor Mac Donnell ; J. Arrowsmith, Lith.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.

From the Irish University Press series of British Parliamentary papers. Facsimile copy of map to originally published as Enclosureno. 3 in Governor Mac Donnell's Despatch no. 41, dated June 16th 1849 in Paper 399 (1849 v. 34).
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain, Parliament., House of Commons.
